baseSize.description: The base size the defines size, space, border radius, and font-size

size.description: Uses the base height to calculate the size scale for each token. Size tokens are used for height and width of an element.

space.description: References the size tokens and defines margin, padding, grid gap, row gap, column gap, and space from: top,bottom,left,right of the elements.

fontSize.description: Uses the base size to caluclate the font-size in rem

fontWeights.description: The weight of the font face.

lineHeight.description: The available line heights represented in unitless values

radii.description: Uses the base size to caluclate the radius in rem

z-index.description: Defines the layering order of elements in the app

offer.description: This layer is reserved only for offers like paywalls, overlays etc

shell.description: This layer is reserved for shell items like the fixed primary nav

ads.description: This layer is reserved for ads not on page

page.description: Any content that is on that main page
